ity opinion on the matter.  Thomas's dissent is worth reading.  He sums it up nicely.\n\nUnfortunately for us as a nation, this kind of fucks us over.  Now, we need a law to be passed.  Fuck, we can't even get the Senate to vote on the SAVE Act.  So I doubt they would pass anything to limit birthright.  We still need to win the midterms.  If we don't it's gonna get really rough around here.\n\nTrump can halt all Visas for pregnant women though.  It's in his wheel house and Constitutionally sound.  Unfortunately, we have millions of baby producers that crossed the border illegally and are here illegally and are popping out demo commie voters by the hundreds.  That's the real issue.", "author": "Badfinz_FL", "created": 1782835229317, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Badfinz_FL", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Trump and the Rubio can now halt all Visa applications for pregnant women.  That effectively ends birthright.  It's really that easy.  The problem is the 17 million illegals that came here under FJB.  They are birthing demo commie voters like rats.  ", "last_comment_created": 1782848171496, "content": "<p>Although I agree with the fact that you can't do this via an EO (what's to stop a demo commie president from nuking your citizenship because you are MAGA for example), I disagree with the majority opinion on the matter.  Thomas's dissent is worth reading.  He sums it up nicely.</p>\n<p>Unfortunately for us as a nation, this kind of fucks us over.  Now, we need a law to be passed.  Fuck, we can't even get the Senate to vote on the SAVE Act.  So I doubt they would pass anything to limit birthright.  We still need to win the midterms.  If we don't it's gonna get really rough around here.</p>\n<p>Trump can halt all Visas for pregnant women though.  It's in his wheel house and Constitutionally sound.  Unfortunately, we have millions of baby producers that crossed the border illegally and are here illegally and are popping out demo commie voters by the hundreds.  That's the real issue.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 17, "score_up": 51, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBhJ1fhY", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 43, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "treason", "id": 8706418, "raw_content": "", "author": "Mddet", "created": 1782838349553, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "KarolineLeavitFucker", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.patriots.win", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBhJ1fhY.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.patriots.win/post/dtFxWAw8UgPe.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/Zeb9bmZ5UtF3OqOT.jpeg", "width": 689, "content-type": "jpeg", "height": 768}], "blurhash": "U5C%Nt_300o}K$M{D$%M00ox~Xk98wIV.9oa", "full_resolution": [1314, 1179]}, "title": "It\u2019s not Trump\u2019s proposal you traitors, it\u2019s WE THE PEOPLE\u2019S proposal!", "last_comment_created": 1782843314212, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 4, "score_up": 43, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": 